[SPEAKER_04]: Less than you.

557
01:05:19,388 --> 01:05:23,149
[SPEAKER_05]: I'll take it.

558
01:05:24,070 --> 01:05:28,391
[SPEAKER_05]: I'm going to try to keep it narrow to three and a half points.

559
01:05:28,831 --> 01:05:30,032
[SPEAKER_05]: Okay.

560
01:05:30,052 --> 01:05:30,472
[SPEAKER_16]: Sounds good.

