659
01:14:52,928 --> 01:14:55,549
[SPEAKER_16]: And like I said, we don't win them all.

660
01:14:55,569 --> 01:14:56,250
[SPEAKER_16]: I don't claim to.

661
01:14:57,490 --> 01:15:01,292
[SPEAKER_16]: We're a municipality and we get sued for whatever reason.

