799
01:27:53,797 --> 01:27:55,738
[SPEAKER_14]: They're almost inevitably never...

800
01:27:59,050 --> 01:28:04,154
[SPEAKER_14]: metrics that can be used to rely on, right, because they're forecasts, and then the realities come in.

801
01:28:05,175 --> 01:28:12,702
