876
01:35:30,244 --> 01:35:30,564
[SPEAKER_05]: All right.

877
01:35:30,965 --> 01:35:33,287
[SPEAKER_05]: Seeing none, we can move to our departments.

878
01:35:35,389 --> 01:35:36,570
[SPEAKER_05]: Let me, one second.

879
01:35:39,133 --> 01:35:40,234
[SPEAKER_16]: I was just going to thank you for your time.

880
01:35:40,254 --> 01:35:45,500
[SPEAKER_16]: President Beers and City Council will be in touch hopefully by the end of day tomorrow and good luck with tonight.

881
01:35:45,700 --> 01:35:45,940
[SPEAKER_16]: Thank you.

882
01:35:49,424 --> 01:35:49,704
[SPEAKER_03]: All right.

