03:05:38,846 --> 03:05:45,051
[SPEAKER_12]: In the public hearing, there was a typo in the variance that,

1948
03:05:46,365 --> 03:05:53,930
[SPEAKER_12]: 1 was a 0 but the difference if you do the math it was 2.183.

1949
03:05:55,151 --> 03:06:06,698
[SPEAKER_12]: And so the next slide will describe kind of how what we are looking at to close that gap.

1950
03:06:06,718 --> 03:06:10,761
[SPEAKER_12]: So we are looking forward to the mayor's budget

1951
03:06:12,886 --> 03:06:22,229
[SPEAKER_12]: that it sounds like, you know, their staff are doing what they can to help us with that gap closure.

1952
03:06:23,870 --> 03:06:35,994
