1971
03:09:45,919 --> 03:09:55,587
[SPEAKER_12]: that and still have, you know, sufficient coverage for content instruction for that EL population.

1972
03:09:56,267 --> 03:10:06,715
[SPEAKER_12]: So, you know, as we have non-renewals and retirements we just, we may not need as many teachers at the high school as we currently have.

1973
03:10:10,058 --> 03:10:12,100
