03:12:40,188 --> 03:12:43,170
[SPEAKER_12]: There's, you know, expenses.

1994
03:12:44,301 --> 03:13:02,370
[SPEAKER_12]: It's all kind of one part of money and I think part of the issue might have been that we originally got at, we originally had added to our budget in the supplemental the full $4 million in FY25.

