1997
03:13:33,392 --> 03:13:36,554
[SPEAKER_12]: but it was for specific purposes.

1998
03:13:37,954 --> 03:13:49,140
[SPEAKER_12]: The longer school day that, you know, before we even talk about raises for teachers, we had to pay for that extra 15 minutes for teachers and paraprofessionals.

1999
03:13:49,901 --> 03:13:54,043
[SPEAKER_12]: Those expenses weren't going to happen until FY 26.

2000
03:13:55,884 --> 03:13:57,825
[SPEAKER_12]: So we came up with a plan to

