2063
03:20:13,571 --> 03:20:34,751
[SPEAKER_20]: So that's just one area where we've really had to look at maybe grant funding or supplemental funding or just creativity within house and kind of look to see what are the priorities for professional development this year, what can we be creative with, what can we use for grant funding or things like that.

