2079
03:22:07,630 --> 03:22:18,702
[SPEAKER_00]: One area the superintendent alluded to that we really want to fund, not that it's professional development, really trying to invest in getting really good professional development.

2080
03:22:20,143 --> 03:22:27,027
[SPEAKER_00]: For our teachers, purchasing and looking at new curriculum if we're hoping to not have to postpone that.

2081
